        <div id="tabs-2">Phasellus mattis tincidunt nibh. Cras orci urna, blandit id, pretium vel, aliquet ornare, felis. Maecenas scelerisque sem non nisl. Fusce sed lorem in enim dictum bibendum.</div>
        <div id="tabs-3">Nam dui erat, auctor a, dignissim quis, sollicitudin eu, felis. Pellentesque nisi urna, interdum eget, sagittis et, consequat vestibulum, lacus. Mauris porttitor ullamcorper augue.</div>
        
    %p
      = 'constraints.inspect = ' + MERCHANT_CONFIG['constraints'].inspect
      
    %p
      = 'product_types.size = ' + MERCHANT_CONFIG['product_types'].size.to_s

    %p
      = 'product_types.inspect = ' + MERCHANT_CONFIG['product_types'].inspect
      
    %p
      = 'product_tags.inspect = ' + MERCHANT_CONFIG['product_tags'].inspect 
    